@Stuckinthebunk1 @SALTisntallowed trivial cost + almost entirely behavioral source = don’t cover it

immense cost + largely non behavioral source = fully cover it

After further consideration i think we should just have a decent yearly dental deductible, and maybe coinsurance

@declairemoore @ATWlover13 @Plasmic_Saul @David_Slotnick Out of pocket max falls under the coinsurance&amp; deductible. 

Copays go towards your out of pocket max but not your deductible. 
Deductible has to be met before your coinsurance applies.

